              "free_text": [
                " The tritons were detected in a 4500-mu-",
                "thick lithium-drifted silicon detector. The defining",
                "aperture of this counter was rectangular and",
                "subtended a solid angle of 1.24e-04 sr. Tritons were",
                "discriminated from other Z=1 reaction products by a",
                "dE-E counter telescope."
              ]
            }
          ],
